<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个妖怪抓住了唐僧，他生气地大喊：“看谁敢伤害我们的大王！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他妖怪走向特勒尔、玛拉和杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空放下金箍棒，看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒和悟净呢？” 他心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净躺在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒揉了揉头：“那些妖怪打倒了我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪走近时，杰克挺起了胸膛：“我不怕你们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他踢了一脚，打了一拳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉大吃一惊：“杰克，你那样不……啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉、杰克和特勒尔突然变得越来越大，比妖怪们大了很多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是怎么回事？” 特勒尔大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他注意到悟空的嘴在动：“是悟空在念咒语吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和玛拉跺着脚踩妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪们四处逃散。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们也可以变大！” 一个妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪们很快变大，抓住了孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些孩子看起来很好吃！” 一个妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人一起变成原来的大小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空向着小妖们走了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西还在按着不断挣扎的黑雨大王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃啊！” 黑雨大王用力一击——咔嚓！他周围的冰碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥着巨大的胳膊，吓了罗西一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 罗西被打到树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转过身：“怎么……啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王把悟空打倒在地上，他很快念起咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咻！传送门打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快走！” 黑雨大王对他的妖怪大军喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的妖怪都进了传送门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们带走了我的朋友们！” 罗西喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有师父！” 八戒大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不能让他们跑了！” 悟净大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也一起进了传送门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道，这里是鸟鸣山！” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王向山上跑去，罗西和悟空在后面追着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！” 唐僧大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪们把唐僧和罗西的朋友们带去另一个方向。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒！悟净！” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们去救他们！我们去消灭黑雨大王！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和罗西找遍了整座山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西皱起眉：“他到底去哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心！” 一块巨石向他们滚来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跳起来避开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王笑了起来，然后暴风雨又来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咬着牙：“我受不了这个妖怪的暴风雨 了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她开始旋转，速度越来越快——罗西变成了龙卷风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空惊讶地张大了嘴巴：“哇！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西旋转上山，把石头和泥土吹得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>暴风雨被吹了回去，打在黑雨大王的脸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 黑雨大王向后摔倒，瓶子掉在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！” 悟空跳到空中，挥起金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！光芒四射，黑雨大王消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只蝾螈趴在他站的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！” 罗西笑着说，“好可爱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一点儿都不可爱。” 悟空说着举起金箍棒，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是妖怪，必须消灭掉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一个声音响起：“不要伤害那只蝾螈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>